{"tid":658601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國豬或成最大贏家】中國加大檢查美國進口豬肉，美企業面臨重大損失","createTime":"2018-05-09T06:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T02:49:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4810e2e02de6423a04ed007d4527a9b29ef1596c","tid":658601,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"據《路透社》引述進口商和行業消息人士指，中國過去幾周已加大對從美國進口豬肉的檢查力度，該舉措可能導致豬肉進口放緩，給美國企業造成重大損失。<br />\n　　<br />\n此舉影響到中國最大的美國豬肉進口商萬洲國際集團（００２８８），該公司是全球最大豬肉加工商，也是美國Ｓｍｉｔｈｆｉｅｌｄ　Ｆｏｏｄｓ的母公司。與此同時，中國對包括水果和木材在內的其他美國農產品的檢查也愈來愈嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述萬洲國際投資者關係主管陳鶴祥稱，「港口對每一艘到港的貨船都要進行開包、檢查，這大大延長了商品在港口停留的時間。相比之下，過去的檢查只是『隨機』進行。」<br />\n<br />\n業內人士認為，在貿易局勢非常緊張的情況下，中國將對其進口產品清單實施一切可能的監管。這樣做有重要的戰略意義，這是北京方面向華盛頓發出的挑釁性警告，以回應美國上周向中國提出的一系列貿易要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280509768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280509768&d=tXfh0r%2FUpTK3OaQPDnQbRwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=554770a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280509768</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f06b85b6a955a1c0054659667d650f36496d6cc","tid":658601,"uid":19557,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c6495cf0d696649b39d8b58f3cbf310a7e3eb8","tid":658601,"uid":57376,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"好呀，一於玩大佢<br />\n民眾喜迎豬肉價狂升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"